Rhett Anthony Bernstein (born 10 September 1987) is an American footballer who plays as a defender.

== Club career ==
Born in San Diego, California, US, Bernstein joined Mjndalen's first-team squad ahead of the 2011 season. He scored his first goals for Mjndalen against Troms on 9 May 2015. They won the game 43.

== Career statistics ==
As of 16 August 2015

